title: HOUR 3- Budda Baker Oct 27, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Budda Baker Oct 27, 2020
description:
Budda Baker tells Dan that while he was running; he was watching himself on the jumbo tron and that Seahawks DK Metcalf was actually closer to him than it appeared. Budda Says that he expects his coach to run that back at least twice in film study with the team, but says it was good that his Cardinals team still got the win.
